item.title: Do you think
item.dc:creator: @ninja_nub ninja nub
item.description:
@ninja_nub wrote:

I wish we can find extraterrestrial life forms. It would be one of the biggest break-through ever recorded. But we’ll probably just do biopsies and kill the poor aliens :(.

Then, I can’t imagine how vast the universe is. Thousands, millions of galaxies, each containing developing stars, living stars living off nuclear fusion, and exploding/collapsing stars. Then theres black holes which just make me think what the hell it’s like in one. And the expanding universe. What happens if we went pass that forbidden barrier? Would god simply strike us down or would there be a syntax error? And it’s extraordinary how it expands at an incredible rate. That means our universe expands so much it probably triples in size a year. And what also creeps me out are those worm holes. What the fuck…? They just magically transport you into the future, past, or some location in the present? This shit makes my brain think to much.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: March 07, 2008, 08:32:03 PM[/size][hr][quote=“Silver Lining, post:8, topic:187067”]Do I think you are a retarded piece of shit? Yes, in fact I do.[/quote]

If you mean step one, agreed.
[center] We get the point. You don’t like step one.[/center]
